  <ul class="list-inline margin-nil">
    <li class="help-redline">&nbsp;</li>
    <li class="help-question">What is YourCandidates.org.uk about?</li>
    <li class="answertext">Many people don't know who they can vote for to represent them in parliament before seeing the ballot paper. Much of the information they have about their candidates comes from marketing, providing an advantage to candidates who are able to pay for it. <a href="/index">YourCandidates.org.uk</a> aims to change this with the power of open data, by providing a neutral source of information about candidates and party policies that is specific to every single constituency.</li>
    <li class="help-redline">&nbsp;</li>
    <li class="help-question">How does it work?</li>
    <li class="answertext" style="margin-bottom: 0px"><a href="/index">YourCandidates.org.uk</a> works by making the content of open data sources easily readable and accessible. As such, we depend on the generosity of the people who work to make these databases available and to improve their quality. The data sources currenly in use are the following:</li>
		<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
		  <li class="answertext-sm"><a href="https://yournextmp.com/">YourNextMP.com</a> is an open, crowdsourced database of general election candidates. <strong>If you see any errors or omissions on this website, you can help improve the database through <A href="https://yournextmp.com/">YourNextMP.com</a>.</strong></li>
		  <li class="answertext-sm"><a href="http://twittelection.co.uk/">TwittElection</a> produces <a href="https://twitter.com/TwittElection/lists">Twitter lists</a> of election candidates.</li>
		  <li class="answertext-sm">The list of party policies is based on our own research. We aim to keep this information up to date as the party manifestos are published.</li>
		  <li class="answertext-sm" style="margin-bottom:40px">The data of YourNextMP.com is licensed under site under the terms of the Creative Commons license <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/">Attribution-ShareAlike (CC-BY-SA)</a>. The candidate images are linked from other sites, and the authors of this website claim no copyright over them.</li>
		</ul>
    <li class="help-redline">&nbsp;</li>
    <li class="help-question">I spy erroneous information on your site!</li>
    <li class="answertext">If you see any errors or omissions on this website, you can help improve the database through <A href="https://yournextmp.com/">YourNextMP.com</a> ++ linkki lomakkeeseen</li>
    <li class="help-redline">&nbsp;</li>
